36struct _libelf_globals _libelf = {
37 .libelf_error = 0,
38 .libelf_fillchar = 0,
39 .libelf_version = EV_NONE
40};
41
42unsigned int
43_libelf_host_byteorder(void)
44{
45 static union {
46 uint32_t val;
47 uint8_t bytes[4];
48 } byte_order_check = {
49 .val = 0xdeadbeef,
50 };
51
52 return (byte_order_check.bytes[0] == 0xef ? ELFDATA2LSB : ELFDATA2MSB);
53}
